These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, water, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: turkish, pakistani, nigerian, colombian, indian, mexican, argentine
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: ice-hockey, water-polo, parkour, sailing, rugby, biathlon, rowing
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, scooter, trike, taxi, roller, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is the colombian##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the pakistani is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the turkish is on the right of the argentine##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the indian##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the skateboard and the mexican##2
 9. the indian is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the car##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the left of the nigerian##1
14. the mexican is the person driving the trike##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the argentine##1
16. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
17. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the nigerian##1
18. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the indian##1
19. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea  | water        | mirinda | hot-chocolate      | lemonade     | cola      | almond-milk     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | colombian         | argentine   | turkish | mexican    | indian | nigerian |
| Sport         | parkour | rugby | ice-hockey | water-polo | rowing  | biathlon  | sailing    |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter         | car     | scooter    | trike | taxi     | skateboard     |

