 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
10. the fan of country is between the fan of r&b and the person eating avocado##2
11. the fan of salsa is the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
13. the fan of folk is between the person eating avocado and the fan of d&b##2
14. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
15. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
16. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
17. the person eating potato is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
18. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
